# {{ project_name }}

Built with the [modo](https://github.com/dmitrymomot/modo) framework.

## Commands

- `just dev` — run dev server with auto-reload
- `just fmt` — format code
- `just lint` — run clippy
- `just test` — run tests
- `just check` — fmt + lint + test
- `just build` — release build

## Conventions

- Handlers, views, and tasks go in separate files (e.g. `handlers/home.rs`, `views/home.rs`, `tasks/send_email.rs`); `mod.rs` contains only `mod` and `pub use` re-exports
